title: Browser Match History Shows a Blank Page.

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body: My Browser match history has been like this for quite awhile now. None of the suggested fixes have worked for me: logging out, clearing cookies, etc. I never had this problem until about 1 month ago or so. Any help would be appreciated!

replies.body:
If [clearing your browser's data](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) or trying another browser didn't resolve this for you, then it's part of a known bug with that page that causes it not to load.

Let me know if you have any questions.
Why does the page break so often and when it does, why does it stay broken for so long?  I'm pretty sure it's broken more than 50% of the times I try to use it.
